SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5716
A bill to amend 1972 PA 230, entitled
"Stille-DeRossett-Hale single state construction code act,"
by amending section 19 (MCL 125.1519), as amended by 2002 PA 721.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 19. (1) The department shall promulgate rules
2 establishing a procedure by which a premanufactured unit intended
3 for use in this state may be issued a certificate of acceptability
4 by the department at its place of manufacture.
5 (2) The procedure shall must require that the manufacturer
6 submit an application to the department with detailed plans and
7 specifications for the premanufactured unit for approval as in
8 compliance with the code. The manufacturer, in accordance with
9 subsection (5), may submit detailed plans and specifications that
