1 of a premanufactured unit with a certificate of acceptability is
2 submitted to an enforcing agency, and if the application, except
3 for the part calling for use of a premanufactured unit with a
4 certificate of acceptability, complies with applicable construction
5 regulations, zoning laws, and local ordinances, the enforcing
